<m0>Reader straightened<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS 2.66 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>out `host' question<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 2 IS 3.68 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS .900 INCHES<m2><ql>
<ql>
<m1><styl>ruleron,n<ql>
